<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS -- French President Jacques Chirac Saturday urged
Yugoslav authorities to bring an end to military operations
against ethnic Albanians in the Serbian province of Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
"If they continue like this, there will be a great risk that
the conflict will spill over into the Balkans," he said.
(France-Kosovo)
</P>
