- - - -
</P>
<P>
ISLAMABAD -- Pakistan Saturday expressed the hope that
U.N. Secretary General Kofi Annan will play a positive role in
promoting peace and security in South Asia through a just
settlement of the Kashmir issue.
</P>
<P>
"We hope the U.N. secretary general will contribute toward the
resolution of the Kashmir dispute in accordance with Security
Council resolutions," a Foreign Office spokesman told a news
conference here Saturday afternoon. (Pakistan-U.N.-India)
