NAIROBI -- Five young ethnic Maasai warriors living in western
Kenya killed a marauding leopard after a five-hour fight Friday to
save a 50-year-old man who was attacked by the wild animal, local
press reported Saturday. (Kenya-Leopard Killed)
</P>
<P>
