over a G-8 Ministerial Communique issued Friday in London, saying
it is "retrogressive and certainly counter productive."
</P>
<P>
"The G-8 decision to work for a postponement in consideration
of loans in the Worlk Bank and other financial institutions is
retrogressive and certainly counter productive," said an official
statement issued Saturday afternoon, although it said the G-8
Ministerial Communique contains some positive elements.
(Pakistan-G-8) 
