<HEADLINE> Jordan's Stock Market Down Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, June 13 (Xinhua) -- Price index in market value on the
Amman Financial Market (AFM), Jordan's sole stock market, closed
Saturday at 172.11 points, down 0.25 point from that on Tuesday,
the AFM daily report said.
</P>
<P>
The market was closed for three days this week on Wednesday,
Thursday and Friday.
</P>
<P>
Total value of trading on Saturday was 635,531 Jordanian
dinars (about 897,643 U.S. dollars), as 496,010 shares changed
hands in 515 carried-out contracts. 
</P>
</TEXT>
