<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Up 9.4 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, June 13 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange index
climbed to 2,163.1 points, up 9.4 points, despite the sluggish
trading over that on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The number of shares that changed hands was 22.83 million in
655 deals, down from 43.94 million shares traded in 1,108 deals
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The value of trading also dived to 4.97 million Kuwaiti dinars
(16.40 million U.S. dollars) from Wednesday's 11.23 million
Kuwaiti dinars (37.06 million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
