<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 13 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 1607.77 points, up 0.36
points over that on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The stock exchange was closed on Thursday and Friday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 2,930,606 shares worth over 9.72 billion rials
(about 1.74 million U.S. dollars) were traded in 826 turns for
386 applicants.
</P>
