no-confidence motion filed against the cabinet of Prime Minister
Ryutaro Hashimoto by three opposition parties.
</P>
<P>
-- Foreign Ministers from the Group of Eight (G-8) major powers
sharply criticized India and Pakistan on Friday for their recent
nuclear tests and proposed a postponement of new loans by
international financial institutions.
</P>
<P>
Asahi, Nihon Keizai:
</P>
<P>
-- The Dow Jones industrial average plunged nearly 160 points
Thursday as a soaring dollar compounded concerns about weakening
trade between Asia and the United States. 
