<HEADLINE> world cup hke -- World Cup Gets First Red Card </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bulgaria and Paraguay played to a goalless draw in the match, the
first game at the France'98 which failed to produce any goal.
</P>
<P>
The Bulgarian team took the upper hand in the first half.
Krassimir Balakov and Hristo Stoitchkov forced Paraguay goal-keeper
Jose Luis Chilavert to make serveral saves.
</P>
<P>
The Bulgarian team missed their best scoring chance at the 35th
minute as Stoitchkov's shot hit the post and bounced out.
</P>
<P>
In the second half, the aging Bulgarian team seemed tired and
the Paraguay team took over the domination of the match.
</P>
<P>
Chilavert almost scored with a free-kick which was blocked by
his Bulgarian counterpart Zdravko Zdravkov. Ed De Goey also missed
several scoring chances.
</P>
<P>
Jorge Campos, who plays for Chinese First Division club Beijing
Guo'an, is the star of the Paraguay team. When he was substituted
at the 77th minute, the crowd appaluded him off the pitch.
</P>
<P>
Two more games will be played on Friday with hosts France take on
South Africa at Marseille and Saudi Arabia play Denmark at Lens.
</P>
