<HEADLINE> Turkish Stock Index Up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
ANKARA, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 4,027.68 points on Friday, up 6.55
points, or 0.17 percent, from that on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The value of the traded shares stood at more than 36 trillion
Turkish liras (about 258 million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
